work_performed: Core structure floors 25-28 rebar tying and forming. Curtain wall installation floors 8-12 south face. MEP rough-in floors 1-6 continuing. Tower crane relocated to position 3 for upper floor steel picks. 185 workers on site.

Concrete pour floors 25-26 - 420 CY pumped. Curtain wall panels 12 units installed south face floors 10-11. Elevator guide rails shaft 1 installation floors 1-15. Interior framing floors 1-4 started. 192 workers on site.

Stripped forms floors 23-24. Rebar tying floors 27-28 continuing. Curtain wall crew moved to east face floors 8-10. Plumbing risers installed shafts A through D floors 1-12. Fire protection piping floors 1-8. 178 workers on site.
safety_incidents: Near miss - falling bolt from crane hook. Bolt landed in exclusion zone. No injury. Crane inspected - worn keeper pin replaced.
delays: Crane shut down 2 hours for inspection and pin replacement

work_performed: Rain day - limited exterior work. Interior activities only: drywall floors 1-3 continued. Electrical rough-in floors 4-6. Tile layout in lobby area. Material staging in parking levels. Safety meeting held for all crews. 85 workers on site.
delays: Full day exterior work stoppage due to rain. Curtain wall and concrete operations postponed.

work_performed: Resumed concrete operations - poured floors 27-28 deck - 380 CY. Curtain wall east face floors 8-9 - 8 panels installed. Roof steel erection started for mechanical penthouse. Drywall finishing floors 1-2. 195 workers on site.

Mechanical penthouse steel erection 60% complete. Core structure forming floors 29-30 started. Curtain wall east face floors 10-12 continuing. Interior mechanical ductwork floors 1-6. Kitchen hood installation Restaurant 1. 188 workers on site.

Concrete pour floors 29-30 - 390 CY. Penthouse steel topped out. Curtain wall north face started floors 8-10. Elevator cab installation shaft 1 began. Sprinkler system testing floors 1-4 passed. Lobby marble floor installation started. 201 workers on site.

Floor 31-32 forming and rebar. Curtain wall north face floors 10-12. Drywall taping and finishing floors 1-3. Guest room framing floors 5-8 started. MEP coordination meeting 2PM - resolved ductwork routing conflict floors 9-10. 198 workers on site.

Floor 31-32 concrete pour - 360 CY. Elevator shaft 2 guide rail installation floors 1-20. Curtain wall west face started floors 8-10. Painting started floors 1-2 common areas. Owner walkthrough of model room floor 5. 185 workers on site.
delays: Material delivery delayed - lobby water feature stone backordered 3 weeks

work_performed: Floor 33-34 forming started. Curtain wall west face continuing. Guest room framing floors 5-8 continuing with bathroom layout. Kitchen equipment delivery for Restaurants 2 and 3 received and staged. Pool deck waterproofing started level 5. 190 workers on site.

Container yard Section D grading and compaction - 8500 SY completed. Crane rail installation berth 3 - 200 LF welded. Electrical ductbank trench excavation substation to berth 2 - 400 LF. Shore power conduit installation berths 1-2. 145 workers on site.

Yard Section D base course aggregate placement - 6200 SY. Crane rail berth 3 welding and alignment check - 180 LF. Substation building concrete block walls courses 1-8. AGV charging station foundation poured - 4 of 12. 152 workers on site.

Crane rail berth 3 completed - final alignment survey passed. Yard Section D concrete paving started - 2400 SY poured. Electrical cable pulling substation to berths 1-2 completed. Terminal OS server room cable tray installation. 148 workers on site.

Rain day - no exterior concrete or paving operations. Interior work only: substation building electrical panel installation. Terminal OS server rack mounting and cabling. Control room console installation. Safety briefing all crews. 62 workers on site.
delays: Full day rain delay - paving and earthwork operations stopped

work_performed: Yard Section D paving resumed - 3200 SY completed. Berth 4 crane rail foundation drilling - 24 anchor holes. STS crane #7 assembly started - boom sections delivered and staged. Shore power transformer installation berth 1. 158 workers on site.

STS crane #7 boom assembly - sections 1-4 connected. Yard Section D paving 85% complete. Berth 4 crane rail foundation grouting - 18 of 24 anchors. AGV navigation marker installation started - 200 of 1200 markers placed. 165 workers on site.

STS crane #7 boom assembly completed - awaiting electrical connection. Yard Section D paving completed. Berth 4 crane rail placement started - 150 LF. Fiber optic cable installation terminal-wide network backbone. 160 workers on site.

STS crane #7 electrical connection and commissioning started. Berth 4 crane rail welding - 280 LF. AGV test track section paved and marked for initial trials. Terminal gate complex steel erection started. 170 workers on site.

Crane #7 commissioning - load test at 50% capacity passed. Gate complex steel framing 40% complete. AGV test vehicle delivered and unloaded. Container tracking sensor installation berths 1-3 - 120 of 400 sensors mounted. 155 workers on site.
delays: Crane #7 software update required - vendor flying in specialist from Rotterdam. 2-day delay to full commissioning.

work_performed: Gate complex steel framing completed. AGV test runs on track section - 8 successful cycles. Berth 4 crane rail welding completed - alignment survey scheduled Monday. Yard lighting installation poles 1-40 of 120. Container scanner assembly at gate. 162 workers on site.
